**The verdict:** If budget is the primary driver and you prefer the quieter white-flash look of diamond optics, start with the [$2,229 lab emerald cut](https://www.bluenile.com/diamond-details/29147824?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational). If you genuinely prefer the rainbow sparkle of moissanite, then moissanite is a valid choice — but know it reads differently in a step cut than it does in photos.

